WEBVTT

00:13.040 --> 00:16.110
[Houde Building]

00:29.830 --> 00:31.290
This case once again shows

00:32.880 --> 00:35.110
that decoding
the criminal's emotional conflict

00:35.110 --> 00:35.790
is key

00:35.790 --> 00:38.280
to understanding
their criminal motivations.

00:38.280 --> 00:40.610
Why are profilers called "mind hunters"?

00:41.320 --> 00:42.380
Because they study

00:42.670 --> 00:43.520
human nature,

00:44.270 --> 00:45.130
the human mind,

00:45.710 --> 00:47.310
and subconscious thoughts.

00:47.840 --> 00:49.700
As I mentioned in the first class,

00:50.890 --> 00:52.620
the best profilers are experts

00:53.150 --> 00:54.840
in psychiatry,

00:55.520 --> 00:56.280
psychology,

00:57.150 --> 00:59.080
especially abnormal psychology,

01:00.200 --> 01:02.000
and have rich hands-on experience

01:02.000 --> 01:03.670
as frontline detectives.

01:07.280 --> 01:10.080
Because they are the people
closest to criminals.

01:11.070 --> 01:13.330
Not necessarily in physical proximity,

01:14.039 --> 01:15.640
but psychologically close.

01:15.990 --> 01:16.600
Of course,

01:18.150 --> 01:20.410
they are also the ones closest to danger,

01:21.870 --> 01:22.480
because

01:27.120 --> 01:28.280
there are two things

01:29.280 --> 01:30.150
in this world

01:30.590 --> 01:32.520
that cannot be stared at directly—

01:33.280 --> 01:34.229
the sun

01:35.070 --> 01:36.200
and the human heart.

01:37.229 --> 01:38.759
The Book of Documents says,

01:39.000 --> 01:41.800
"The human heart
is perilous and unpredictable."

01:50.590 --> 01:52.350
Today is my last class here.

01:53.780 --> 01:54.979
There is one question

01:56.430 --> 01:58.630
I've always wanted to talk to you about.

01:59.509 --> 02:01.380
When we deal with criminals,

02:02.600 --> 02:03.800
if we look too deeply,

02:04.470 --> 02:06.130
we might see our own darkness,

02:06.640 --> 02:08.169
even perverse psychology.

02:10.030 --> 02:11.680
How should we remain calm?

02:21.400 --> 02:23.200
When the abyss gazes back at you,

02:23.850 --> 02:24.780
don't be afraid.

02:26.079 --> 02:27.340
We must firmly believe

02:28.430 --> 02:30.230
that we are different from them.

02:31.740 --> 02:34.000
The love, warmth, and beauty of humanity

02:34.620 --> 02:35.280
we have felt

02:35.960 --> 02:37.160
throughout our lives

02:37.910 --> 02:39.640
will form a light in our hearts.

02:42.030 --> 02:43.890
No matter how dark a room we enter,

02:44.360 --> 02:45.490
we must never forget

02:46.630 --> 02:48.160
to bring this light with us.

04:07.750 --> 04:13.310
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

04:13.790 --> 04:16.120
[Episode 28]

04:20.630 --> 04:23.190
Jiang Hansheng!

04:42.000 --> 04:43.240
Jiang Cheng?

04:44.120 --> 04:46.120
How could I forget about you?

04:46.750 --> 04:49.240
We could have been friends.

05:30.070 --> 05:30.750
Chief Tan,

05:30.920 --> 05:31.950
this is Jiang Hansheng.

05:31.950 --> 05:32.960
If we keep searching like this,

05:32.960 --> 05:34.220
we won't find Zhou Jin.

05:34.540 --> 05:35.690
We need to do the opposite now

05:35.690 --> 05:36.750
and put pressure on him,

05:36.750 --> 05:37.750
making him think we have already

05:37.750 --> 05:39.120
taken control of the whole situation

05:39.120 --> 05:40.390
and that it makes no difference
whether he's there or not.

05:40.390 --> 05:41.190
By then,

05:41.310 --> 05:42.560
he will definitely

05:42.560 --> 05:44.159
try to grasp at his last straw

05:44.270 --> 05:45.800
He will go look for Zhou Jin.

05:46.000 --> 05:47.130
How certain are you?

05:47.390 --> 05:48.870
Qi Yan's filthy intention is just

05:48.870 --> 05:51.010
to torture me to death
in front of Zhou Jin.

05:51.010 --> 05:52.170
Or do that to her in front of me.

05:52.170 --> 05:54.380
When he reaches a dead end,

05:54.420 --> 05:55.950
he will definitely do that.

05:59.270 --> 06:00.290
Jiang Cheng, Jiang Cheng.

06:00.290 --> 06:01.880
Find a way to let Qi Yan go.

06:02.350 --> 06:03.950
Let him lead us to Zhou Jin.

06:26.680 --> 06:27.280
Hansheng.

06:27.440 --> 06:28.050
Qi Yan,

06:28.920 --> 06:29.520
let her go!

06:30.000 --> 06:32.130
Officer Zhou, I advise you not to move.

06:32.530 --> 06:33.970
Otherwise,

06:34.960 --> 06:36.820
it would be very dangerous for us—

06:37.790 --> 06:38.790
for both of us.

06:39.720 --> 06:40.600
Hansheng—

06:41.390 --> 06:43.590
do you like it when people call you that?

06:44.040 --> 06:45.070
Hansheng.

06:47.510 --> 06:49.240
Do you really think you've won?

06:51.630 --> 06:53.870
The game isn't over yet.

06:54.920 --> 06:56.750
Let's move on to the final part.

06:57.480 --> 06:58.360
I promise that

06:58.630 --> 07:00.760
as long as you finish this game with me,

07:01.000 --> 07:02.440
and I'll let your Officer Zhou go.

07:02.440 --> 07:04.320
I promise. I swear.

07:05.360 --> 07:06.560
You have two choices:

07:08.030 --> 07:09.720
shoot me dead

07:13.680 --> 07:15.950
and let me die along with Officer Zhou,

07:17.070 --> 07:17.800
or...

07:18.750 --> 07:20.430
shoot

07:21.310 --> 07:22.230
yourself.

07:25.290 --> 07:27.680
Pay with your life for my brother's.

07:29.390 --> 07:31.160
What will you choose?

07:32.100 --> 07:33.560
I'm looking forward to it.

07:35.190 --> 07:36.280
Come on!

07:36.830 --> 07:38.000
Jiang Hansheng!

07:38.159 --> 07:40.000
Make your choice!

07:40.800 --> 07:41.480
Hansheng!

07:41.480 --> 07:42.480
Don't care about me!

07:42.480 --> 07:43.480
Pull the trigger!

07:43.720 --> 07:45.630
Pull the trigger! Don't care about me!

07:45.630 --> 07:46.560
Right.

07:46.560 --> 07:48.420
Listen to what Officer Zhou says.

07:48.480 --> 07:50.560
She's so worried about your safety.

07:50.560 --> 07:51.630
Hansheng,

07:51.630 --> 07:52.690
what should you do?

07:53.290 --> 07:55.780
Do you want Officer Zhou to die?

07:56.800 --> 07:57.510
Come on.

07:58.159 --> 07:59.760
Make your choice, Hansheng!

08:00.190 --> 08:01.510
Be decisive!

08:01.630 --> 08:02.920
You didn't hesitate at all

08:02.920 --> 08:04.450
when you killed my brother.

08:05.000 --> 08:06.120
Now!

08:06.440 --> 08:08.760
For the girl you love,

08:09.630 --> 08:12.070
sacrifice yourself!

08:12.950 --> 08:13.870
Qi Yan,

08:15.990 --> 08:18.250
I think you've been wrong about one thing

08:19.260 --> 08:21.260
from the start.

08:22.030 --> 08:22.810
I...

08:23.930 --> 08:25.930
didn't come here to be your hostage.

08:28.290 --> 08:29.220
I...

08:31.370 --> 08:32.770
came here to avenge...

08:34.110 --> 08:35.230
my brother.

08:45.580 --> 08:46.540
Jiang Hansheng.

08:48.530 --> 08:49.460
Jiang Hansheng!

08:50.650 --> 08:51.710
My name is Zhou Jin.

08:52.030 --> 08:52.790
From now on,

08:53.030 --> 08:54.160
we're good friends.

08:54.670 --> 08:55.930
No one can bully you anymore.

08:55.930 --> 08:57.360
Officer Jiang!

09:02.100 --> 09:03.100
Protect Zhou Jin.

09:04.270 --> 09:05.600
I must protect Zhou Jin.

09:05.910 --> 09:06.550
Zhou Jin.

09:07.890 --> 09:09.620
I hope you won't get hurt again.

09:10.750 --> 09:11.720
In the future,

09:11.820 --> 09:13.550
I'll definitely face dangers.

09:14.390 --> 09:16.160
But the more dangerous a place is,

09:16.160 --> 09:18.360
the greater the opportunity it offers.

09:19.510 --> 09:20.770
I will protect myself.

09:21.550 --> 09:22.200
Zhou Jin,

09:23.510 --> 09:24.270
I love you.

09:26.730 --> 09:28.260
When I first met you,

09:29.870 --> 09:31.000
I wanted to have you.

09:33.080 --> 09:34.030
Jiang Hansheng.

10:01.000 --> 10:01.830
Junior!

10:01.940 --> 10:02.740
Hurry! Hurry!

10:02.760 --> 10:03.730
Junior! Hurry!

10:04.430 --> 10:05.590
Stretcher! Hurry!

10:05.750 --> 10:06.550
Give him a hand!

10:06.550 --> 10:07.590
Careful.

10:07.840 --> 10:08.630
Careful.

10:09.150 --> 10:09.650
Careful.

10:09.650 --> 10:10.310
Be careful.

10:12.400 --> 10:13.400
Be careful.

10:24.720 --> 10:26.190
This person is extremely dangerous

10:26.190 --> 10:27.520
and mentally unstable.

10:27.790 --> 10:28.670
Sniper team,

10:28.850 --> 10:29.850
stay alert.

10:41.000 --> 10:42.240
Jiang Hansheng.

10:43.240 --> 10:44.750
You think you won, right?

10:45.080 --> 10:47.240
You think I'll give up like this?

10:47.840 --> 10:49.200
Jiang Hansheng!

10:49.440 --> 10:51.030
Where is Qi Zhen?

10:51.370 --> 10:53.530
Tell her to come and see me!

10:54.790 --> 10:56.270
Before your trial,

10:57.910 --> 10:59.510
I'll let her come and see you.

11:22.000 --> 11:22.660
Don't move!

11:37.030 --> 11:38.910
Haven't you always wanted to know

11:39.390 --> 11:41.240
how Zhou Chuan died?

11:48.150 --> 11:48.870
Zhan Wei,

11:49.870 --> 11:50.800
just wait to die.

12:36.140 --> 12:36.730
Zhou Jin,

12:37.140 --> 12:37.940
you're awake?

12:38.480 --> 12:39.740
I'll go get the doctor.

12:43.390 --> 12:44.190
What's wrong?

12:46.000 --> 12:47.030
Silly.

12:48.360 --> 12:49.750
From such a high place,

12:51.480 --> 12:53.410
you just jumped without thinking?

12:54.630 --> 12:56.560
I should be the one asking you that.

12:57.930 --> 12:58.740
From now on,

13:00.740 --> 13:02.270
it's my turn to protect you.

13:04.980 --> 13:06.780
You did a good job protecting me.

13:08.620 --> 13:10.550
I really want to kiss you right now.

13:12.120 --> 13:13.200
But right now,

13:14.510 --> 13:16.570
it seems inconvenient for me to do it.

13:37.320 --> 13:38.920
The sun is really nice today.

13:45.910 --> 13:47.970
And we're wearing matching outfits.

13:49.600 --> 13:51.240
Let's try not to wear matching outfits

13:51.240 --> 13:52.900
like this again in the future.

13:56.770 --> 13:58.030
I'll go get the doctor.

14:03.220 --> 14:04.820
She's basically stable now.

14:05.020 --> 14:05.730
But

14:05.850 --> 14:07.030
she still needs to be hospitalized

14:07.030 --> 14:08.500
for observation for a while.

14:08.500 --> 14:09.870
After all, when she fell into the water,

14:09.870 --> 14:11.680
her internal organs were damaged.

14:11.680 --> 14:13.340
And she was in a coma for 3 days.

14:15.840 --> 14:17.240
I was in a coma for 3 days?

14:17.330 --> 14:17.970
Yes.

14:18.440 --> 14:19.640
Get some proper rest.

14:19.880 --> 14:20.940
Thank you, doctor.

14:25.790 --> 14:26.870
It has been 3 days?

14:27.870 --> 14:29.270
How is everything going?

14:30.030 --> 14:31.030
What about Qi Yan?

14:32.340 --> 14:34.070
Qi Yan was arrested on the spot.

14:35.150 --> 14:36.200
He got his karma.

14:38.040 --> 14:39.040
What about Qiu Ye?

14:40.780 --> 14:42.510
She was dead when she was found.

14:43.300 --> 14:44.540
But you saved her son.

14:51.630 --> 14:54.090
Your mentor asked me
to pass a message to you.

14:55.270 --> 14:56.040
What...

14:59.230 --> 15:00.460
What did he say?

15:02.310 --> 15:03.360
He said well done.

15:03.870 --> 15:04.930
You did a great job.

15:06.400 --> 15:07.620
It's all over.

15:08.480 --> 15:10.030
The nightmare of the 8/17 Case

15:10.030 --> 15:10.960
is over.

15:18.670 --> 15:19.360
Zhou Jin,

15:20.670 --> 15:22.080
cry if you want to.

15:40.870 --> 15:41.670
It's all over.

15:47.510 --> 15:48.480
It's all over.

16:01.310 --> 16:01.860
Dad,

16:02.550 --> 16:03.120
Mom.

16:04.870 --> 16:05.720
Chuan's case

16:06.200 --> 16:07.030
is solved.

16:07.710 --> 16:09.240
It was the drug traffickers

16:09.510 --> 16:11.840
who colluded with Zhan Wei and killed him.

16:16.950 --> 16:17.950
It's been 6 years.

16:18.610 --> 16:19.940
I never expected

16:19.970 --> 16:21.450
the result to be like this.

16:23.550 --> 16:24.200
Dad,

16:24.870 --> 16:25.790
are you okay?

16:28.030 --> 16:29.030
We are fine.

16:29.640 --> 16:31.830
Your brother was an upright man.

16:31.970 --> 16:34.170
He always thought the best of everyone.

16:35.030 --> 16:35.630
Dad,

16:36.200 --> 16:37.800
he had always been like this.

16:38.960 --> 16:39.960
Since he was a kid,

16:41.000 --> 16:42.120
he has always

16:42.840 --> 16:44.640
set high standards for himself.

16:45.740 --> 16:47.340
Right now, he probably hopes

16:47.790 --> 16:48.720
our whole family

16:49.270 --> 16:50.600
can be proud of him.

16:51.620 --> 16:53.220
I'm definitely proud of him.

16:54.200 --> 16:55.390
Your brother

16:55.410 --> 16:56.520
is my pride.

16:58.360 --> 16:59.200
Zhou Jin,

17:00.160 --> 17:01.560
you are also my pride.

17:20.349 --> 17:21.609
My dad just praised me.

17:23.000 --> 17:24.260
That made you so happy?

17:25.000 --> 17:25.829
Of course.

17:26.440 --> 17:28.030
I was praised twice today.

17:28.640 --> 17:29.920
My mentor praised me,

17:30.010 --> 17:31.410
and my dad praised me too.

17:32.430 --> 17:33.720
They are not like you.

17:34.030 --> 17:35.830
Hearing them praise me is harder

17:35.920 --> 17:37.850
than getting a first-class merit.

17:40.160 --> 17:41.760
Have you called your family?

17:42.490 --> 17:43.490
They are abroad.

17:44.880 --> 17:45.790
I plan to visit

17:46.270 --> 17:47.200
the Prof later.

17:48.150 --> 17:49.110
I'll go with you.

17:49.310 --> 17:50.030
No need.

17:50.050 --> 17:51.250
Get some proper rest.

17:52.550 --> 17:53.310
Sir,

17:53.680 --> 17:55.400
remember to go downstairs
to get the test report.

17:55.400 --> 17:55.880
Okay.

17:56.000 --> 17:56.600
Thank you.

17:59.070 --> 17:59.800
I'll go then.

18:00.000 --> 18:01.060
Don't move around.

18:12.790 --> 18:14.310
Zhou Jin, how do you feel?

18:14.310 --> 18:15.240
Feeling better?

18:16.550 --> 18:17.750
I'm fine. I'm doing great.

18:17.750 --> 18:18.810
I'm already awake.

18:30.030 --> 18:30.790
You're here?

18:34.950 --> 18:35.880
Are you alright?

18:37.000 --> 18:37.590
I'm fine.

18:41.590 --> 18:42.590
Zhan Wei...

18:42.640 --> 18:43.570
tried to escape,

18:44.110 --> 18:45.370
and I brought him back.

18:57.200 --> 18:58.600
Where is Jiang Hansheng?

19:00.200 --> 19:01.260
He went downstairs

19:01.550 --> 19:03.000
to get my test report.

19:04.640 --> 19:05.440
Good husband.

19:08.830 --> 19:10.430
Your hair is getting longer.

19:14.790 --> 19:16.030
After I get back to Haizhou,

19:16.030 --> 19:17.290
I should get a haircut.

19:18.200 --> 19:19.400
Actually, it's fine.

19:20.240 --> 19:21.570
Long hair is quite nice.

19:21.720 --> 19:23.780
Aren't you having your wedding soon?

19:26.880 --> 19:28.030
Will you...

19:29.350 --> 19:30.410
come to my wedding?

19:32.310 --> 19:33.240
I don't think so.

19:35.000 --> 19:37.130
I'm not as generous as Jiang Hansheng.

19:37.310 --> 19:38.480
I might not be able to stop myself

19:38.480 --> 19:39.780
from punching his smug face.

19:39.780 --> 19:40.640
Don't you dare.

19:41.830 --> 19:42.510
Okay.

19:43.030 --> 19:43.830
I won't dare.

19:48.160 --> 19:49.920
I'm going back to Haizhou this afternoon.

19:49.920 --> 19:50.590
Chief Tan

19:50.590 --> 19:52.200
submitted my ID documents.

19:52.590 --> 19:53.920
The higher-ups need to ask

19:53.920 --> 19:55.450
about Cangfeng operation.

19:55.720 --> 19:57.980
I have to go back and cooperate with them.

19:59.030 --> 19:59.960
Do it properly.

20:01.500 --> 20:03.100
If there's anything I can do,

20:03.270 --> 20:04.240
you must tell me.

20:10.550 --> 20:11.310
Jin.

20:14.110 --> 20:15.550
I never meant to hurt you.

20:16.720 --> 20:18.240
About the past,

20:19.160 --> 20:21.620
I just never found a chance
to explain to you.

20:23.590 --> 20:24.270
Forget it.

20:25.350 --> 20:26.880
It's all in the past anyway.

20:29.260 --> 20:30.590
Now you have the chance.

20:33.590 --> 20:35.390
I want to hear your explanation.

20:41.480 --> 20:42.550
Before me,

20:43.350 --> 20:45.270
Yao actually sent an undercover agent.

20:45.270 --> 20:46.880
In less than a month,

20:46.880 --> 20:48.340
his identity was exposed.

20:48.680 --> 20:50.070
After that mission failed,

20:50.070 --> 20:51.510
Yao planned to arrange for me

20:51.510 --> 20:53.240
to be the next undercover agent.

20:53.240 --> 20:54.270
But we just couldn't find

20:54.270 --> 20:56.000
a chance to infiltrate safely.

20:56.640 --> 20:58.700
Creating a fake identity takes time.

20:59.240 --> 21:00.510
To avoid any slip-ups,

21:00.510 --> 21:02.830
it requires patient
and meticulous planning.

21:02.830 --> 21:05.360
So Cangfeng operation
kept getting delayed.

21:07.060 --> 21:12.190
[2012]

21:07.270 --> 21:10.240
At the time, I was in the Criminal Investigation Brigade 2
of Fengzhou District.

21:10.240 --> 21:12.280
My style of handling cases
was known for being tough.

21:12.280 --> 21:13.310
As you know,

21:13.680 --> 21:15.140
I offended a lot of people.

21:16.000 --> 21:16.920
One day,

21:17.030 --> 21:19.200
my middle school classmates
suddenly contacted me.

21:19.200 --> 21:20.410
They said it had been a long time

21:20.410 --> 21:22.440
and wanted to get together for a meal.

21:22.440 --> 21:23.370
But it turned out

21:23.640 --> 21:24.550
to be a trap.

21:26.000 --> 21:27.730
All of them had been bought off.

21:28.200 --> 21:30.160
They started messing with me
at the dinner table,

21:30.160 --> 21:31.270
got me drunk,

21:31.590 --> 21:33.250
and set me up with a honey trap.

21:34.790 --> 21:35.960
Their original plan was

21:35.960 --> 21:37.350
to take me to a hotel

21:37.590 --> 21:39.750
and then report me
to the Public Security Brigade,

21:39.750 --> 21:41.410
posing as ordinary citizens,

21:41.570 --> 21:44.000
so I would no longer be able to
remain a police officer.

21:44.000 --> 21:45.790
But I have a high tolerance for alcohol,

21:45.790 --> 21:47.390
so I woke up halfway through.

21:50.590 --> 21:53.160
I originally planned
to leave the hotel right away.

21:53.160 --> 21:54.220
But then I realized

21:54.440 --> 21:55.750
this was the opportunity

21:55.750 --> 21:57.150
Yao had been waiting for.

21:57.350 --> 21:58.150
Yao,

21:58.170 --> 21:58.970
listen to me.

21:59.550 --> 22:01.720
There's been an unexpected situation,

22:01.720 --> 22:02.680
but I think

22:02.920 --> 22:04.450
this is a good opportunity.

22:06.480 --> 22:07.880
I'm in a hotel right now.

22:08.270 --> 22:09.680
I was set up with a honey trap.

22:09.680 --> 22:10.480
Don't worry.

22:10.880 --> 22:12.810
I've got that woman under control.

22:13.360 --> 22:14.990
I think we should

22:15.010 --> 22:17.010
use this opportunity and play along

22:17.110 --> 22:18.310
to carry out our plan.

22:20.740 --> 22:22.540
It really is a good opportunity.

22:24.030 --> 22:26.160
That criminal gang has always been

22:26.790 --> 22:28.310
extremely vigilant

22:28.310 --> 22:29.510
towards new members.

22:29.760 --> 22:31.060
Rather than letting them find out

22:31.060 --> 22:32.310
my identity as a police officer,

22:32.310 --> 22:33.960
it's better to tell them from the start

22:33.960 --> 22:35.160
that I used to be a cop.

22:36.070 --> 22:37.750
Using this honey trap scheme,

22:37.750 --> 22:39.720
Yao turned me into an unlucky guy,

22:39.900 --> 22:41.160
who was about to be promoted

22:41.160 --> 22:43.690
but was framed
from within the organization.

22:44.350 --> 22:46.210
Yao told me not to leave the hotel.

22:46.480 --> 22:49.030
He said he would plant
a bag of drugs in the evidence

22:49.030 --> 22:50.550
and use illegal drug possession

22:50.550 --> 22:52.070
to send me to Guhua Prison,

22:52.400 --> 22:53.540
giving me a chance

22:53.570 --> 22:55.160
to approach He Wen openly.

22:57.960 --> 22:59.760
Everything was going smoothly,

23:01.160 --> 23:02.020
except for you.

23:08.920 --> 23:10.480
Making me believe all this

23:13.440 --> 23:14.900
must have been quite hard.

23:19.830 --> 23:21.350
The interrogation Yao arranged

23:21.350 --> 23:23.550
was staged specifically for you to see.

23:23.740 --> 23:26.090
The evidence chain was solid,

23:27.160 --> 23:29.090
and everything was well prepared.

23:30.090 --> 23:31.920
It wasn't difficult before the verdict,

23:31.920 --> 23:34.680
since you had to recuse yourself
during the investigation phase.

23:34.680 --> 23:36.830
The hard part started after sentencing,

23:36.830 --> 23:38.480
when you always insisted on seeing me.

23:38.480 --> 23:39.940
I really couldn't take it,

23:41.640 --> 23:43.040
so I could only avoid you.

23:43.710 --> 23:45.710
Even when we met, I didn't say a word.

24:10.880 --> 24:12.160
Do you regret it?

24:17.640 --> 24:20.040
Zhou Chuan's cause of death
has been found,

24:21.790 --> 24:24.140
and you aren't crying
as much as you used to.

24:24.140 --> 24:25.000
It was worth it.

24:30.400 --> 24:32.600
You really are the person I used to like.

24:33.050 --> 24:33.770
Of course.

24:43.370 --> 24:44.000
Alright.

24:44.020 --> 24:44.880
I should go now.

24:45.800 --> 24:47.040
Your Professor Jiang

24:47.060 --> 24:48.240
may have been pretending

24:48.240 --> 24:49.850
to be wandering around outside
several times.

24:49.850 --> 24:50.980
If I stay any longer,

24:50.990 --> 24:52.920
we might actually end up fighting.

25:42.120 --> 25:44.180
The memory card from Qi Yan's camera.

25:55.000 --> 25:56.040
I don't know why,

25:56.120 --> 25:57.120
but it burned out.

25:58.230 --> 25:59.560
I had someone look at it.

25:59.640 --> 26:01.020
It's completely broken.

26:01.020 --> 26:02.620
The data can't be recovered.

26:06.380 --> 26:07.070
Thank you.

26:08.300 --> 26:09.960
No need to be so polite with me.

26:14.880 --> 26:16.340
Take good care of Zhou Jin.

26:17.880 --> 26:18.810
I always do.

27:25.740 --> 27:29.550
♪ Waiting for a surging blue ♪

27:29.670 --> 27:31.670
♪ Tide ♪

27:32.680 --> 27:33.480
Jin.

27:33.060 --> 27:35.880
♪ Passing through the thorny ♪

27:33.480 --> 27:34.140
Take a look.

27:34.240 --> 27:35.040
Am I handsome?

27:35.130 --> 27:35.920
Yes.

27:36.110 --> 27:36.920
Take a look.

27:36.320 --> 27:39.430
♪ Forest ♪

27:37.030 --> 27:37.830
So handsome.

27:38.160 --> 27:39.560
This outfit looks great.

27:39.960 --> 27:43.430
♪ Discovering that it's always ♪

27:41.030 --> 27:42.280
I look great or this outfit does?

27:42.280 --> 27:43.190
Am I handsome?

27:43.350 --> 27:44.200
Didn't I tell you?

27:43.810 --> 27:47.340
♪ A desolate, silent place ♪

27:44.560 --> 27:45.880
This outfit looks great!

27:45.880 --> 27:46.590
Me or the outfit?

27:46.590 --> 27:47.250
The outfit!

27:47.400 --> 27:48.160
The outfit!

27:47.980 --> 27:51.590
♪ Finally, being able to embrace ♪

27:50.160 --> 27:51.070
I was wrong!

27:51.350 --> 27:51.790
Me or the outfit?

27:51.790 --> 27:52.510
Sorry, sorry.

27:52.330 --> 27:54.280
♪ The dawn ♪

27:52.510 --> 27:53.440
Me or the outfit?

27:54.490 --> 27:57.520
♪ Listening from afar ♪

27:57.900 --> 28:01.280
♪ Who is crying? ♪

28:01.780 --> 28:04.780
♪ The brush outlines the color red ♪

28:05.200 --> 28:08.630
♪ Whose joy is that? ♪

28:08.950 --> 28:12.310
♪ If the door hasn't opened yet ♪

28:12.630 --> 28:16.450
♪ After running for so long ♪

28:14.270 --> 28:15.000
Jiang Cheng.

28:15.550 --> 28:16.810
Is this a "love" brand?

28:16.870 --> 28:18.860
♪ In the swirling memories ♪

28:16.920 --> 28:18.160
Let me see what material it is.

28:18.160 --> 28:19.110
Don't touch it.

28:19.110 --> 28:20.880
My girlfriend knitted this
stitch by stitch.

28:19.670 --> 28:22.860
♪ Who's clearer? ♪

28:20.880 --> 28:22.070
Who are you to touch it?

28:22.070 --> 28:23.960
Our Officer Jiang
was taken down so easily.

28:23.790 --> 28:26.860
♪ Who were those words meant for? ♪

28:24.000 --> 28:24.640
I like it.

28:24.640 --> 28:25.750
Is it any of your business?

28:25.750 --> 28:26.480
No, it isn't.

28:27.170 --> 28:30.800
♪ Waiting for the wind
to stop for a moment ♪

28:27.270 --> 28:27.920
Boss,

28:28.480 --> 28:29.470
are you really not hot?

28:29.470 --> 28:30.550
Not at all.

28:30.820 --> 28:34.300
♪ At that time, things were unclear ♪

28:32.310 --> 28:34.400
Zheyi, turn on the AC.

28:34.590 --> 28:35.270
Okay.

28:34.740 --> 28:37.800
♪ Yet I keep looking back at it ♪

28:38.080 --> 28:39.450
♪ Maybe it was ♪

28:39.490 --> 28:40.570
♪ A beating heart ♪

28:40.590 --> 28:41.480
♪ Chasing the light, searching for you ♪

28:41.500 --> 28:42.590
♪ Who's shining bright ♪

28:42.660 --> 28:45.280
♪ But where are you? ♪

28:46.130 --> 28:48.700
♪ Will what we once had ♪

28:48.720 --> 28:52.030
♪ Eventually be lost? ♪

28:52.630 --> 28:55.770
♪ Who will tell me? ♪

29:07.100 --> 29:09.900
♪ Listening to the ticking
of the second hand ♪

29:09.960 --> 29:10.510
Jin,

29:10.510 --> 29:12.200
don't write these

29:10.940 --> 29:13.400
♪ It's like a riddle ♪

29:12.200 --> 29:13.000
meaningless letters anymore.

29:13.000 --> 29:13.660
You hear me?

29:14.520 --> 29:17.860
♪ After seeing through it, it's only ♪

29:15.070 --> 29:15.880
Why?

29:16.310 --> 29:18.440
Why won't you let me
write letters anymore?

29:18.440 --> 29:19.880
Do you like someone else now?

29:18.530 --> 29:21.360
♪ A matter of a few millimeters ♪

29:20.790 --> 29:22.480
I'm telling you to study hard.

29:21.910 --> 29:24.980
♪ If the window is always closed tight ♪

29:22.750 --> 29:23.720
I don't care about that.

29:23.720 --> 29:24.510
Just tell me.

29:24.830 --> 29:26.720
If you say you have someone
in your heart now,

29:25.580 --> 29:29.280
♪ Cutting off all connections,
in the end ♪

29:26.830 --> 29:28.310
I'll never write to you again.

29:28.310 --> 29:28.960
I don't.

29:28.960 --> 29:29.690
How could...

29:29.730 --> 29:32.130
♪ In this world, is there anyone ♪

29:30.200 --> 29:31.000
I don't.

29:31.880 --> 29:32.750
Then have you read all the letters

29:32.430 --> 29:35.130
♪ Smarter than anyone else? ♪

29:32.750 --> 29:33.550
I wrote to you?

29:35.590 --> 29:36.400
I have.

29:36.300 --> 29:39.880
♪ Who were those words meant for? ♪

29:38.310 --> 29:40.250
Then recite a couple of lines for me.

29:40.020 --> 29:43.380
♪ Waiting for the wind
to stop for a moment ♪

29:43.530 --> 29:46.630
♪ At that time, things were unclear ♪

29:47.140 --> 29:50.630
♪ Yet I keep looking back at it ♪

29:50.810 --> 29:52.360
♪ Maybe it was ♪

29:52.380 --> 29:53.200
♪ A beating heart ♪

29:53.230 --> 29:54.070
♪ Chasing the light, searching for you ♪

29:54.070 --> 29:54.950
♪ Who's shining bright ♪

29:55.330 --> 29:58.220
♪ But I'm here ♪

29:58.990 --> 30:01.230
♪ Will what we once had ♪

30:01.260 --> 30:06.290
♪ Eventually be lost? ♪

30:07.930 --> 30:13.970
♪ Who will tell me? ♪

30:20.550 --> 30:21.280
Jiang Cheng,

30:21.480 --> 30:23.050
the higher-ups have responded.

30:23.050 --> 30:23.870
They offered you

30:23.870 --> 30:25.220
2 choices.

30:44.350 --> 30:45.650
Have you made up your mind?

30:45.650 --> 30:46.580
I have.

30:48.400 --> 30:49.530
You won't regret it?

30:51.440 --> 30:52.130
Chief Tan,

30:52.330 --> 30:53.240
since when did you become

30:53.240 --> 30:54.440
so naggy?

31:06.340 --> 31:09.200
[Meng Junfeng]

31:06.750 --> 31:08.210
This is your new identity.

31:27.490 --> 31:28.220
Jiang Cheng,

31:29.300 --> 31:29.970
remember,

31:30.830 --> 31:33.090
the deaths of Leader Yao and Meng Junfeng

31:33.480 --> 31:35.010
have nothing to do with you.

31:35.500 --> 31:37.430
Don't pressure yourself too much.

31:37.640 --> 31:38.440
I understand.

31:39.270 --> 31:41.400
I just constantly remind myself

31:41.580 --> 31:42.710
that no matter what,

31:42.790 --> 31:43.920
I must live on.

31:46.890 --> 31:48.350
There is a long road ahead.

31:50.720 --> 31:51.920
You must be careful.

31:58.030 --> 31:59.790
Did you say goodbye to Zhou Jin?

32:00.160 --> 32:01.070
No need.

32:01.830 --> 32:04.560
We might have a chance
to meet again in the future.

32:07.480 --> 32:08.160
Chief Tan,

32:08.750 --> 32:10.460
here is my operation report
for the past 5 years.

32:10.460 --> 32:11.860
All the details are in it.

32:12.020 --> 32:13.150
And there's a file.

32:20.740 --> 32:22.440
[Report on 8/17 Case Special Operation]

32:25.880 --> 32:28.080
Fortunately, I did not fail my mission.

32:28.550 --> 32:30.950
The task has been successfully completed.

32:31.720 --> 32:33.520
I will continue to move forward.

32:33.830 --> 32:34.830
Report complete.

32:35.880 --> 32:38.140
I will always remain loyal to my country,

32:38.200 --> 32:39.070
my people,

32:39.880 --> 32:40.830
my beliefs,

32:41.660 --> 32:42.730
and...

33:15.670 --> 33:18.390
Based on Qi Yan's case,
the lab is preparing

33:18.540 --> 33:20.260
to launch a new project

33:21.100 --> 33:22.400
on criminal psychology research

33:22.400 --> 33:26.130
and the prevention and control
of juvenile crime.

33:26.790 --> 33:28.950
The team will include Shen

33:29.680 --> 33:31.550
and your junior, Zhuang Ming.

33:32.350 --> 33:33.230
You'll need to

33:33.420 --> 33:35.500
guide and support them in the future.

33:36.600 --> 33:38.260
I'll share everything I know.

33:38.430 --> 33:39.160
That's good.

33:42.200 --> 33:43.550
After a while,

33:44.700 --> 33:46.160
I will completely retire.

33:48.170 --> 33:49.690
I'll go back

33:49.790 --> 33:52.290
and spend time
with my little granddaughter,

33:52.290 --> 33:53.480
counting ducks.

33:54.850 --> 33:55.680
From now on,

33:56.060 --> 33:58.060
it'll be the era of you young people.

33:58.600 --> 33:59.800
Keep up the good work.

34:01.790 --> 34:02.960
Tan said

34:04.070 --> 34:06.160
your quick decisions at the scene

34:07.470 --> 34:08.670
saved a lot of people.

34:11.920 --> 34:14.850
Prof, it's been a long time
since you last praised me.

34:14.949 --> 34:16.350
Look at you getting smug.

34:25.880 --> 34:26.510
Prof,

34:28.139 --> 34:29.540
I'm going back tomorrow.

34:34.920 --> 34:35.590
Go back.

34:38.790 --> 34:40.050
You should go home now.

34:51.590 --> 34:52.190
Stop.

34:54.760 --> 34:55.480
Take it off.

34:57.139 --> 34:57.970
Take it off.

35:07.800 --> 35:08.460
Put it on me.

35:15.550 --> 35:16.810
Where are the pockets?

35:18.140 --> 35:18.960
Why are you laughing?

35:18.960 --> 35:19.760
You look good.

35:20.070 --> 35:22.870
Wait. When people
wear this kind of coat nowadays,

35:23.440 --> 35:24.840
does it look better buttoned up,

35:24.840 --> 35:25.480
or

35:26.670 --> 35:27.670
worn open?

35:29.030 --> 35:30.960
Buttoned up looks more energetic.

35:31.840 --> 35:33.240
There's only one button?

35:34.600 --> 35:35.810
How is it? Looks good?

35:35.840 --> 35:36.400
Totally.

35:36.550 --> 35:37.710
Let me walk a few steps for you to see.

35:37.710 --> 35:38.230
Okay.

35:44.360 --> 35:45.670
Come on, follow me.

35:47.810 --> 35:48.900
I'll unbutton it.

35:48.930 --> 35:49.670
Look.

35:50.360 --> 35:51.560
-How do I look?
-Prof.

35:51.640 --> 35:52.390
Just wear this

35:52.390 --> 35:54.000
to attend Zhou Jin and my wedding.

35:54.000 --> 35:54.900
Definitely.

35:54.920 --> 35:56.380
I will definitely wear it.

35:58.320 --> 35:59.520
The color is too dark.

36:06.760 --> 36:08.240
Full of youthful energy.

36:11.060 --> 36:12.430
This is the new intern

36:12.450 --> 36:13.860
in our squad,

36:14.070 --> 36:15.000
Gao Yaojie.

36:15.230 --> 36:16.150
From today on,

36:17.270 --> 36:18.470
you'll be his mentor.

36:20.310 --> 36:21.710
Nice to meet you, Senior.

36:22.070 --> 36:22.760
Senior,

36:22.990 --> 36:24.710
I also graduated
from Jingzhou Police Academy.

36:24.710 --> 36:26.370
Please guide me in the future.

36:29.560 --> 36:30.160
Comrades,

36:30.190 --> 36:32.050
let me introduce a new colleague,

36:32.280 --> 36:32.920
Gao Yaojie.

36:32.920 --> 36:34.120
Just call him Yaojie.

36:35.000 --> 36:36.230
This is Liu.

36:36.670 --> 36:37.450
Hello, Liu.

36:37.470 --> 36:37.940
Hello.

36:38.320 --> 36:39.000
Bai Yang.

36:39.320 --> 36:41.050
We all call him Little Bai Yang.

36:41.420 --> 36:42.360
Since a newcomer is here,

36:42.360 --> 36:43.920
I can't be Little Bai Yang anymore, right?

36:43.920 --> 36:44.780
So Old Bai Yang?

36:45.560 --> 36:46.290
Bai.

36:46.550 --> 36:48.030
Just call me Yaojie in the future.

36:48.030 --> 36:48.760
Look at him.

36:48.760 --> 36:50.020
He has a bright future.

36:50.730 --> 36:51.480
Lu Pengfei.

36:51.760 --> 36:52.440
Senior Lu.

36:52.550 --> 36:53.550
Hello, Senior Lu.

36:53.640 --> 36:54.290
Yaojie.

36:54.320 --> 36:55.840
Try to talk to him
as little as possible unless necessary.

36:55.840 --> 36:56.840
Come on, let's continue the introduction.

36:56.840 --> 36:57.510
Jun.

36:58.330 --> 36:59.660
Wan Chongshan, Mr. Wan.

36:59.880 --> 37:00.550
Gao Yaojie.

37:00.870 --> 37:01.870
I've heard of you.

37:02.270 --> 37:03.650
You're a good young man.
Keep up the good work.

37:03.650 --> 37:04.910
Zhou Jin, you're back?

37:05.000 --> 37:05.920
Dan.

37:06.110 --> 37:06.670
You came just in time.

37:06.670 --> 37:07.590
Let me introduce you.

37:07.590 --> 37:08.230
Yaojie.

37:08.320 --> 37:09.250
Say hello to Dan.

37:09.360 --> 37:10.110
Hello, Dan.

37:10.280 --> 37:11.030
Hello.

37:11.720 --> 37:13.780
Are... are you close to your due date?

37:14.330 --> 37:14.850
Yes.

37:16.150 --> 37:17.150
How are you doing?

37:17.320 --> 37:18.700
Don't do anything reckless

37:18.700 --> 37:20.300
until you recover, alright?

37:20.360 --> 37:21.440
I'm perfectly fine.

37:21.440 --> 37:22.110
I reported for duty today

37:22.110 --> 37:23.030
and started working immediately.

37:23.030 --> 37:24.720
I can even show you

37:24.750 --> 37:26.150
a one-handed handstand right now.

37:26.150 --> 37:26.800
Alright.

37:26.830 --> 37:27.830
I will

37:27.950 --> 37:29.440
assign you more tasks then.

37:29.440 --> 37:31.170
How have things been recently?

37:31.560 --> 37:34.130
The Jingzhou police started with
Qi Yan and Zhan Wei

37:34.130 --> 37:35.710
and pulled on a loose thread
that unraveled the whole fabric.

37:35.710 --> 37:36.710
The entire Dongsheng Group

37:36.710 --> 37:38.020
is now under investigation.

37:38.020 --> 37:40.070
Just the case files alone are this much.

37:40.070 --> 37:40.670
Yeah.

37:41.280 --> 37:42.440
I'm from Jingzhou.

37:42.920 --> 37:44.280
Now everyone there

37:44.280 --> 37:45.410
is talking about it.

37:45.440 --> 37:46.570
You're from Jingzhou?

37:46.570 --> 37:49.030
Then why did you come here
for an internship?

37:49.510 --> 37:50.670
Because of Uncle Yao.

37:50.670 --> 37:51.750
Who? Uncle Yao?

37:53.380 --> 37:54.090
Leader Yao?

37:55.800 --> 37:57.230
When I was in the police academy,

37:57.230 --> 37:59.360
I was sponsored by Uncle Yao all along.

37:59.550 --> 38:00.950
He was like a father to me.

38:01.710 --> 38:02.670
You might think

38:02.690 --> 38:04.750
I'm being a bit childish saying this,

38:05.190 --> 38:07.590
but since Uncle Yao
died in the line of duty,

38:07.670 --> 38:09.940
the only way I can repay him

38:10.190 --> 38:11.510
is to carry on his will

38:12.080 --> 38:13.480
and strive to be a good police officer.

38:13.480 --> 38:14.630
That's the spirit!

38:14.840 --> 38:17.040
As your senior, I have to say a few words.

38:17.400 --> 38:18.230
Alright, that's enough.

38:18.230 --> 38:20.290
He just got here today. Go easy on him.

38:21.760 --> 38:23.090
It's so good to be young.

38:23.550 --> 38:26.380
I was the champion
in the police academy combat competition.

38:26.380 --> 38:28.670
Uncle Yao even came to school
to watch me receive the award.

38:28.670 --> 38:29.670
So that means...

38:30.330 --> 38:32.330
you must be pretty good at fighting.

38:32.670 --> 38:33.920
Then you're in luck.

38:34.190 --> 38:34.840
Zhou Jin,

38:35.190 --> 38:35.990
Officer Zhou,

38:36.320 --> 38:37.580
once won second place.

38:38.230 --> 38:39.360
Keep it low-profile.

38:39.360 --> 38:40.320
It's in the past.

38:40.440 --> 38:42.240
If there's a chance, we can spar.

38:43.030 --> 38:44.560
No, do it right now. Come on.

38:45.090 --> 38:45.780
Senior,

38:46.070 --> 38:47.480
I'm not looking down on you.

38:47.480 --> 38:48.320
Men and women

38:48.320 --> 38:50.490
have differences in physical fitness.

38:50.490 --> 38:50.850
Well...

38:50.850 --> 38:52.910
I... I'm just afraid I might hurt you.

38:53.880 --> 38:55.840
Now I can't accept that. Come on.

38:57.670 --> 38:59.130
I really can't stand this.

38:59.920 --> 39:00.510
Three,

39:00.840 --> 39:01.440
two,

39:01.460 --> 39:02.060
one!

39:02.290 --> 39:03.330
Professor Jiang?

39:10.630 --> 39:12.480
You're back to being a police officer
again?

39:12.480 --> 39:13.800
Under the leadership
of the Provincial Bureau,

39:13.800 --> 39:14.800
a new crime research lab
is being established

39:14.800 --> 39:16.440
at the Haizhou Public Security Bureau.

39:16.440 --> 39:18.970
It will be
officially inaugurated tomorrow.

39:20.000 --> 39:22.800
Then we should call you Director Jiang
from now on.

39:22.880 --> 39:24.140
Just call me Hansheng.

39:26.000 --> 39:28.260
I'm used to calling you Professor Jiang.

39:29.320 --> 39:31.180
You can call me whatever you want.

39:34.030 --> 39:35.190
I'm used to...

39:35.190 --> 39:36.850
calling you Professor Jiang.

39:37.550 --> 39:39.120
You can call me whatever you want, babe.

39:39.120 --> 39:40.480
He didn't say babe!

39:40.510 --> 39:41.710
Don't talk nonsense!

39:42.230 --> 39:42.840
Wait.

39:44.440 --> 39:45.710
I think the baby is coming!

39:45.710 --> 39:47.030
Hurry! Get her to the hospital!

39:47.030 --> 39:48.550
Don't panic!

39:48.570 --> 39:49.860
Call an ambulance!

39:50.320 --> 39:51.150
I'll drive her there.

39:51.150 --> 39:51.710
Be careful!

39:51.710 --> 39:52.280
Drive her there.

39:52.280 --> 39:53.010
Don't panic!

39:53.190 --> 39:53.920
Don't panic!

39:54.110 --> 39:54.920
Purse, phone—

39:54.940 --> 39:55.880
bring them all.

39:55.880 --> 39:56.900
Hansheng, drive the car.

39:56.900 --> 39:57.840
Hansheng, drive the car.

39:57.840 --> 39:58.800
Be careful!

39:58.800 --> 39:59.590
To the hospital! To the hospital!

39:59.590 --> 40:00.440
Be careful!

40:00.600 --> 40:01.250
Don't panic!

40:01.250 --> 40:01.770
Dan!

40:10.280 --> 40:11.400
I remember our first date

40:11.400 --> 40:12.710
was right here.

40:15.760 --> 40:18.160
Back then,
they only had a small cart stall.

40:20.190 --> 40:21.540
It was April then,

40:22.070 --> 40:23.320
and you bought me ice cream.

40:23.320 --> 40:24.230
I was freezing.

40:25.200 --> 40:26.340
I was dressed too formally,

40:26.340 --> 40:27.400
and I was so nervous

40:27.590 --> 40:29.190
that I was sweating all over.

40:29.440 --> 40:31.670
I thought you were taking revenge on me
on purpose.

40:31.670 --> 40:33.070
I was late, wasn't I?

40:33.230 --> 40:35.230
I was 5 hours late for our first date.

40:35.590 --> 40:36.070
No.

40:36.880 --> 40:38.480
I was really happy back then.

40:38.670 --> 40:40.840
You were out on a mission all day
and it was so late,

40:40.840 --> 40:42.570
but you still came out to see me.

40:48.070 --> 40:49.870
What would you two like to drink?

40:51.330 --> 40:52.660
A milk tea with 30% sugar

40:52.920 --> 40:53.720
and extra boba, please.

40:53.720 --> 40:54.280
Okay.

40:56.440 --> 40:57.030
Sir,

40:57.130 --> 40:58.340
you look familiar.

40:59.280 --> 41:01.280
You've been here
with your girlfriend before?

41:01.280 --> 41:02.210
I'm his wife now.

41:04.120 --> 41:05.050
Coming right up.

41:13.990 --> 41:14.990
The sunset today

41:15.260 --> 41:16.260
is so beautiful.

41:18.230 --> 41:18.770
Yeah.

41:19.670 --> 41:20.360
So pretty.

41:44.160 --> 41:47.020
I remember you used to say
the sunset was beautiful.

41:47.710 --> 41:49.370
Where exactly is that sunset?

41:49.590 --> 41:51.050
You never took me to see it.

41:54.670 --> 41:55.600
It's right here.

42:14.280 --> 42:15.280
This sunset

42:15.620 --> 42:16.820
is really beautiful.

42:21.800 --> 42:23.060
The wind is picking up.

42:47.090 --> 42:53.770
[Among all the sunsets, secrets,
and regrets, I'm glad I have you]

42:55.830 --> 42:58.310
[The End]
